&lt;li&gt;Experience of shipping production-grade ML/AI systems at scale, with deep understanding of ML infrastructure, model serving, and MLOps best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills with the ability to collaborate effectively across Engineering, Product, and Design organizations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
