&lt;p&gt;AI is moving fast and Stripe is moving fast to adopt it. But we need to make sure we do all of this safely, and for most of these tools, enterprise-grade security isn&#39;t just available off the shelf. That&#39;s where the AI security team comes in—we&#39;re responsible for building and partnering to create the right security primitives to enable Stripe to move fast safely.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a team that works in the low-level components of our AI stack, so both infrastructure and security experience are pluses. This space is moving fast, so being comfortable with ambiguity and changes in priority is a must.&lt;/p&gt;
