&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Develop and apply statistical and machine learning models to solve key marketing challenges, including audience targeting, creative effectiveness, customer engagement, and campaign performance measurement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Assess the incremental impact of marketing investments across channels to inform budget allocation and growth strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
