&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Translate complex analyses into clear recommendations for marketing leaders and executive stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Drive foundational improvements in data quality, measurement infrastructure, and reporting capabilities across the marketing organization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Identify new opportunities to improve marketing effectiveness and influence strategic planning through data-driven insights.&lt;/li&gt;
