&lt;li&gt;Build simulation environments and replay infrastructure for agent training and evaluation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Orchestrate distributed training and distributed RL with Ray, including scheduling, scaling, and failure recovery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish rigorous automated benchmarks and regression tests for world model predictions, agent performance, and simulation fidelity&lt;/li&gt;
